    "description": "<strong>《时空三分之三 Tritime Space》</strong>是一款根据音乐节拍进行动作打击、炫酷技能释放的单机打怪闯关游戏：<br>1.你能从世界中感知律动，从而强化你的攻击，并且，可以搭配律动和按键组合出不同的技能输出方式！<i>--律动就是能量，难道不是吗？</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/ba9c171c2d2299a984c2a8bf8bcebfc2.poster.avif?t=1724237072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/ba9c171c2d2299a984c2a8bf8bcebfc2.webm?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/ba9c171c2d2299a984c2a8bf8bcebfc2.mp4?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>2.有多个炫酷技能可以获取，技能也能搭配合适的律动时机能造成强力伤害！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/893fc8ba47c7d4949d522ab10f9c2805.poster.avif?t=1724237072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/893fc8ba47c7d4949d522ab10f9c2805.webm?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/893fc8ba47c7d4949d522ab10f9c2805.mp4?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>3.疯狂的敌人将无情想你攻击，敌人也将释放强力技能打击你，并且每个地图系列都有对应的boss，能释放更强的技能，难度更高、当然击败敌人后将获取更丰富的奖励！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/098187d8a91b86242fd4d531b20260eb.poster.avif?t=1724237072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/098187d8a91b86242fd4d531b20260eb.webm?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/098187d8a91b86242fd4d531b20260eb.mp4?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>4.随着地图关卡和进度，你将解锁更强的技能，并且随着等级提升，你能强化你喜欢的技能，你能否驱散敌人？<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/d091d17beac1781067ff29f6f6d1c73e.poster.avif?t=1724237072\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/d091d17beac1781067ff29f6f6d1c73e.webm?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3127630/extras/d091d17beac1781067ff29f6f6d1c73e.mp4?t=1724237072\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
